*** IMPORTANT: The C Object System requires GNU make 3.80 or higher ***

Compilation and run:
--------------------

from each subdirectories:

make

or (assuming COS is installed or LD_LIBRARY_PATH is set appropriately):

make debug
./arch/bin/cos-ex01_d

Examples:
---------

ex01:
  Show how to create classes and extend a class cluster (i.e. Stream)

ex02:
  Show how to use multiple inheritance (i.e. File)
  
ex03:
  Show how to implement a "manual" garbage collector in few lines on top of
  ownership retain and release.

Debugging makefiles:
--------------------

make [target] SHOW=yes TRACE=yes

# debug flags
SHOW  will show the commands run
TRACE will show the value of important variables

